## `.gitignore`（中英文註解）

```gitignore
# 忽略所有原始資料集檔案 (請勿上傳) / Ignore all raw dataset files (Do NOT upload)
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.json
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.docx

# Jupyter Notebook 檢查點 / Notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Python 快取檔 / Python cache files
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# VSCode 與其他編輯器設定 / Editor settings
.vscode/
*.swp

# 作業系統產生檔 / OS-generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# 圖片與輸出（若非必要請勿上傳） / Images and outputs (avoid uploading unless necessary)
*.png
*.jpg

# 分析結果（如不想版本控可加上）/ Analysis outputs (add if you don't want to version control)
analysis_results.json

# 你可依需求再自行擴充 / Add more rules as needed
